  <section class="docstring">


        <div class="specs">
          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">Orddict1 = Orddict2 = <a href="#t:orddict/2">orddict</a>(Key, Value)</pre>

        </div>


<p>Appends a new <code class="inline">Value</code> to the current list of values associated with <code class="inline">Key</code>.</p><p>An exception is generated if the initial value associated with <code class="inline">Key</code>
is not a list of values.</p><h2 id="append/3-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#append/3-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">OrdDict1</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">orddict</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-2">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-3">{</span><span class="ss">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-4">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-4">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-3">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-2">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-5">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-6">{</span><span class="ss">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-7">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-7">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-6">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-5">]</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="n">OrdDict2</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">orddict</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">append</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-8">(</span><span class="ss">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">OrdDict1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-8">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-9">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-10">{</span><span class="ss">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-11">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-11">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-10">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-9">]</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">3&gt; </span><span class="n">OrdDict3</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">orddict</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">append</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-12">(</span><span class="ss">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">OrdDict2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-12">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-13">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-14">{</span><span class="ss">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-15">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-15">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-14">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-13">]</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">4&gt; </span><span class="nc">orddict</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">append</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-16">(</span><span class="ss">y</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">OrdDict3</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4876657518-16">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
