        </div>


<p>Removes the item with key <code class="inline">Key</code> from dictionary <code class="inline">OrdDict1</code>.</p><h2 id="erase/2-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#erase/2-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">OrdDict1</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">orddict</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-2">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-3">{</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-3">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-4">{</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-4">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-2">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-5">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-6">{</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-6">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-7">{</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-7">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-5">]</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="nc">orddict</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">erase</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-8">(</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">OrdDict1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-8">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-9">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-10">{</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-10">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-9">]</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">3&gt; </span><span class="nc">orddict</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">erase</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-11">(</span><span class="ss">z</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">OrdDict1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4127994666-11">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
