  <section class="docstring">


        <div class="specs">
          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">Increment = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:number/0">number</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Orddict1 = Orddict2 = <a href="#t:orddict/2">orddict</a>(Key, Value)</pre>

        </div>


<p>Adds <code class="inline">Increment</code> to the value associated with <code class="inline">Key</code> and store this value.</p><p>If <code class="inline">Key</code> is not present in the dictionary, <code class="inline">Increment</code> is stored as
the first value.</p><h2 id="update_counter/3-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#update_counter/3-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">OrdDict1</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">orddict</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-2">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-3">{</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-3">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-4">{</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-4">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-2">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-5">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-6">{</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-6">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-7">{</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-7">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-5">]</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="n">OrdDict2</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">orddict</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">update_counter</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-8">(</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">OrdDict1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-8">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-9">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-10">{</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-10">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-11">{</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-11">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-9">]</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">3&gt; </span><span class="n">OrdDict3</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">orddict</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">update_counter</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-12">(</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">OrdDict2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1661242580-12">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
